dct_title_s: Les chemins vers Saint-Jacques de-Compostelle = Routes of Santiago de Compostela in France. Institut national de l'information géographique et forestière ; [en partenariat avec l'Association de coopération inter-régionale des chemins de Saint-Jacques de Compostelle].
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and contours. Includes legend in French and English, color photographs and historical and culture texst,  3 inset maps Includes inset map of Corsica, ancillary map of Western Europe and North Africa and ancillary map of the northwestern portion of the Iberian peninsula. "Tracé national des chemins vers Saint-Jacques de Compostelle, lieux historiques et de légende, sites naturels et patrimoine culturel bâti" "National Santiago Pilgrim Way routes, Historic and legendary places, Natural sites and cultural heritage buildings"
dct_creator_sm: Institut national de l'information géographique et forestière (France).
